[[File:Victoria.jpg|thumb|250px|The victoria.]]
The '''victoria''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of plant that could be found floating on some rivers of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]].

On one occasion, the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]] surfed on a victoria while enjoying a summer day with his friends [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]], [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]], and [[Latara/Legends|Latara]].

